      "span_text": "To analyze the circadian expression of a gene that peaks at a different phase than CCR2 , TOC1 RNAi constructs were used to transform Arabidopsis plants expressing the morning-phased clock-controlled reporter CAB2 :: luc [CITATION_1] ."
